Package: wbstats
Type: Package
Title: Programmatic Access to Data and Statistics from the World Bank API
Description: Tools for searching and downloading data and statistics from
  the World Bank Data API (<http://data.worldbank.org/developers/api-overview>)
  and the World Bank Data Catalog API (<http://data.worldbank.org/developers/data-catalog-api>).
Version: 0.2.1.9000
